name: SONG FOR @ArchitectureNFT
description:
-SOUND ON-

Cifu (@ArchitectureNFT) is an artist with a focus on experimental architecture in the digital space. He is a “manija” of the crypto-world, and help me with so many data about this chaotic-beautiful world. He has an amazing collection called LIGHT, and it´s inspired by Kase.O´s theme, Becquer. He invited me to do the sound design in that collection. And for this special song he asked me to do something related with that, this is what I did. My re-interpretation about the poetic meaning of Kase.O beautiful song, and on the cover, I keep some powerful phrase from the original song that resonate with me plus a wink to the work of Cifu and the video of Kase.O. As always, I try to do something sincere, with love & dedication.

Dibaxu // tw: @dibaxuP

*This is a collection of special and dedicated song for those collectors that get #1, #2, #3 and #4 for my “Annotations” collection. If you get it, let me know and I will do something special for you, this is a lifetime offer.
